    "Moreover, Accessibility was not in focus in any of the studies we identified, even though it is among the goals for the target group of model developers (Arrieta et al. 2020).",
    "Furthermore, the target groups of regulators, managers and model developers are not adequately addressed, only being mentioned in a single study that tried to cater to many target users in theory, but which did not implement a working prototype (Braines et al. 2019).",
    "The answers provided by recent work are largely based on a template-filling approach, which limits their adaptability to a specific type of user question and disturbs the perception of natural dialogue.",
    "While it is often stated as a goal for future work that natural language generation techniques can be used to align the answer to the specific user question, it is an open question whether the impact of that would be meaningful.",
    "Almost every system targets a \"Why\" question to explain a system's decision."
